# Zed-cafe export tree schema

Applies when editing export/import paths, inbox JSON, gojs memfs, or zed-cafe Playwright gates. See skill `wanix-zed-cafe-export`, rule `wanix-vm-lifecycle.mdc`.

## Single owner

**`zss/feature/wanix/zedcafetreeschema.ts`** owns:

| Symbol | Use |
|--------|-----|
| `kebabcasezedcafedirname(name, id)` | Folder segment `{kebab-name}-{id}`; empty name → `id` only |
| `readzedcafebookprefix` / `readzedcafepageprefix` | Export path prefixes |
| `validatezedcafeexportpaths` | Export/push guard — returns `{ ok, errors[] }` |
| `assertzedcafeexportvalid` | Tests / `buildzedcafeexportfiles` — throws on failure |
| `ZED_CAFE_EXPORT_ALLOWED_PATH` | Canonical regex allowlist — mirrored in `ops/fixtures/wanix/zed-cafe/allowed-path-patterns.json` for Go guest FS |

Canonical **ids** stay in `stats.json` bodies; folder names are for browsing only.

## Folder layout (breaking)

```text
zed-cafe/stats.json
books/<kebab-name>-<bookId>/stats.json
books/.../pages/<kebab-name>-<pageId>/stats.json
  board/, object/, terrain/, charset/, palette/ (unchanged leaf names)
```

Examples: `demo-book1`, `player-page2`, id-only fallback `sid_abc`.

## Validation policy

| Path | Schema guard |
|------|--------------|
| `buildzedcafeexportfiles` | `assertzedcafeexportvalid` at end |
| `runzedcafeexport`, `pushzedcafeexportfiles`, `encodezedcafeinboxjson` | `validatezedcafeexportpaths` — **fail closed** (`apilog` + skip write) |
| `parsezedcafeexportfiles` / guest import | **No** allowlist — permissive for stray files; resolve dirs via `kebabcasezedcafedirname` from meta names |
| Guest FS create (`#task/<rid>/export`, `#ramfs/zed-cafe` ns bind) | `schemaguardfs.go` — reject `Create`/`Mkdir`/`Rename`/`Symlink` outside allowlist |

## Required wiring

- Export: `wanixstateexport.ts` uses `readzedcafebookstatspath` / `readzedcafepageprefix` — never `books/${book.id}/pages/${page.id}`.
- Import: `wanixstateimport.ts` opens `books/${kebabcase(name)}-${id}/…` from root + book meta — **no** legacy `books/<id>/` resolution.
- Push: `wanixzedcafe.ts` validates before `putwanixfile` and before inbox encode.

## Go ExportFS boundary

`ops/fixtures/wanix/zed-cafe/exportfs.go` hydrates inbox JSON into guarded memfs (`schemaguardfs.go`). Path allowlist is embedded from `allowed-path-patterns.json` (must match `ZED_CAFE_EXPORT_ALLOWED_PATH` in TS — Jest parity test). Guest `Create`/`Mkdir`/`Rename`/`Symlink` outside the allowlist return `ErrPermission`. Host push remains TS-only (`validatezedcafeexportpaths` before inbox encode).

VM `#ramfs/zed-cafe` stages via ns bind from guarded `#task/<rid>/export` (`appendzedcafeexportramfsbind`), not per-file ramfs blob copies.

## Prohibited

- Ad-hoc export path strings outside `zedcafetreeschema.ts`
- A second validation/coordination layer wrapping push (rule `no-new-systems-for-bugs.mdc`)
- Importing `WANIX_ZED_CAFE_EXPORT_FILE` into `zedcafetreeschema.ts` (circular dep — use `ZED_CAFE_EXPORT_PATH_FILE` locally)
- Re-adding legacy `books/<id>/` import
- Production fallback binds to paper over invalid trees (`#task/export` → `#ramfs/zed-cafe` as schema workaround)

## Unit tests

Always pass **`--config ops/jest.config.ts`** (bare `yarn jest` on `.ts` tests fails Babel `import type`).

```bash
yarn jest --config ops/jest.config.ts \
  ops/tests/unit/feature/wanix/zedcafetreeschema.test.ts \
  ops/tests/unit/feature/wanix/wanixstateexport.test.ts \
  ops/tests/unit/feature/wanix/wanixstateimport.test.ts \
  ops/tests/unit/feature/wanix/wanixiframechildmount.test.ts --no-coverage
```

Composite gate: `yarn task run wanix:zed-cafe:memfs:validate`.
